item.title: About
item.description: Tech U is currently an internal-only technical workforce education program that brings new L4 talent into AWS and teaches them the soft and hard skills needed to be field-ready and to successfully work with AWS customers as Solutions Architects(SAs), Professional Services (PS) Consultants, and Technical Trainers (TTs). Tech U, which launched in 2017, is now a dedicated program within Training and Certification (T&C) and has expanded to six global cohorts, with a charge to find and develop diverse and inclusive cloud talent globally.
